/* AI workflow preset prompts (full text seeded into the chat composer
   when the user clicks a preset). The English key is the canonical
   prompt the LLM sees for English-locale users; the Chinese value is
   what Chinese-locale users see in their composer (and edit before
   sending). The LLM understands both languages equally well. */
"Find every filler word in the transcript (uh, um, you know, like, so, etc.) and remove them." = "找出转写里所有口癖词（uh、um、嗯、啊、那个、就是 等）并删除。";
"Identify every distinct voice in the video and label who says what." = "识别视频里的每一位说话人，并在转写文本中标注每句话是谁说的。";
"Identify each speaker in the video, then mute every line spoken by <fill in which speaker>." = "识别视频里的每一位说话人，然后把 <填入哪位说话人> 说的每一句台词静音。";
"Identify each speaker in the video, then list every line spoken by <fill in which speaker>." = "识别视频里的每一位说话人，然后列出 <填入哪位说话人> 说过的每一句话。";
"List every span in the video where no face is visible on screen." = "列出视频里画面中没有人脸的所有时间段。";
"Find every span that is near-black or looks like the lens was covered." = "找出视频里所有接近黑屏或看起来镜头被遮住的时间段。";
"Review the current cut and mark the moments where a B-roll clip or visual overlay would strengthen the story." = "复看当前剪辑，标出适合插入 B-roll 素材或视觉叠层来增强叙事的时刻。";
"Suggest 3 English title candidates based on the transcript." = "基于转写内容，给出 3 个候选标题。";
"Review the current cut and pick 3–5 moments best suited for a ChapterTitle animated title card (chapter starts, topic shifts, emphasis sections, etc.). First list each suggestion with: composed_time (seconds), title, optional subtitle, theme (dark/light/accent), and a brief reason. After the user confirms, call the generate_overlay tool for each accepted suggestion (template_id=\"ChapterTitle\", props_json filled per the fields above, durationSeconds defaults to 2.5). After generation, remind the user they can double-click the overlay in the Inspector to fine-tune copy or theme." = "审视当前剪辑，挑出 3–5 个最适合插入 ChapterTitle 动画标题卡的时间点（章节开头、话题切换、强调段落等）。先用列表给出每个建议：composed_time（秒）、title、可选 subtitle、theme（dark/light/accent），并简述理由。等用户确认后，对每个被采纳的建议调用 generate_overlay 工具（template_id=\"ChapterTitle\"，props_json 按上述字段填，durationSeconds 默认 2.5）。生成后提醒用户可以双击 overlay 在 Inspector 里继续微调文案或主题。";
"Write a 3-4 sentence English summary of the current video." = "用 3–4 句话总结当前视频的内容。";
"Pick the best opening hook (cold-open teaser) from the recordings. Call score_hook_candidates with top_k=5, present the candidates with their punch reasoning so I can pick one, and after I confirm a choice call add_hook_teaser with that candidate's source_video_id, source_start, and source_end. Do not pick or apply automatically — always wait for my reply." = "在所有素材里给我挑一条最有冲击力的开场金句。先调 score_hook_candidates（top_k=5），把候选清单连同理由读给我听让我挑哪一条；我确认之后再调 add_hook_teaser（参数从我挑中的那条取 source_video_id / source_start / source_end）。不要自己替我挑或者直接 apply——每一步都等我回答。";
"Add bilingual subtitles. Detect the source language of the current subtitles: if it is Chinese, translate every cue to English; otherwise translate every cue to Simplified Chinese. Then enable bilingual style with the translation rendered below the original at 75% size." = "添加双语字幕。识别当前字幕的源语言：若是中文，则把每一条字幕翻译成英文；否则翻译成简体中文。然后启用双语样式，把译文以 75% 字号显示在原文下方。";
"Translate every subtitle cue to English, then enable bilingual style with the English translation below the original at 75% size." = "把每一条字幕翻译成英文，然后启用双语样式，把英文译文以 75% 字号显示在原文下方。";
"Translate every subtitle cue to Simplified Chinese (zh-Hans), then enable bilingual style with the Chinese translation below the original at 75% size." = "把每一条字幕翻译成简体中文，然后启用双语样式，把中文译文以 75% 字号显示在原文下方。";
"Translate every subtitle cue to <fill in target language>, then enable bilingual style with the translation below the original at 75% size." = "把每一条字幕翻译成 <填入目标语言>，然后启用双语样式，把译文以 75% 字号显示在原文下方。";

